<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 20:06:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯表示回应加沙停火提议，要求全面停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-responded-to-gaza-truce-proposal-demands-total-cease-fire/0000018e-d8c6-df04-adae-fdd6696c0000</link><description>然而，以色列消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列尚未收到证实哈马斯说法的信息。在伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的儿子被杀以及与伊朗的紧张关系日益加剧之后，以色列很难决定此时是否有可能推进该协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 19:37:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-responded-to-gaza-truce-proposal-demands-total-cease-fire/0000018e-d8c6-df04-adae-fdd6696c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加强紧急措施，下令关闭学校以应对伊朗袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-intensifies-emergency-measures-orders-school-shutdown-amid-iranian-threat/0000018e-d8b8-de1f-a38f-debfbd4a0000</link><description>教育部宣布“从周日开始，取消所有教育活动”，直至另行通知；全国范围内聚会人数限制在1000人以内</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 18:59:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-intensifies-emergency-measures-orders-school-shutdown-amid-iranian-threat/0000018e-d8b8-de1f-a38f-debfbd4a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列青少年被谋杀、定居者在巴勒斯坦村庄肆虐后，以色列国防军加强了西岸部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/idf-beefs-up-west-bank-force-after-israelis-murder-settler-riots-in-palestinian-villages/0000018e-d864-de1f-a38f-de7f4a580000</link><description>据以色列军方称，数十名以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸冲突中受伤。整个星期六，在发现一名被谋杀的 14 岁以色列人的尸体后，一群定居者进入巴勒斯坦村庄并放火焚烧房屋</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 18:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/idf-beefs-up-west-bank-force-after-israelis-murder-settler-riots-in-palestinian-villages/0000018e-d864-de1f-a38f-de7f4a580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战第 190 天：伊朗称扣押了“与以色列有关”的船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-190-iran-says-it-seized-ship-linked-to-israel/0000018e-d862-d01b-abdf-f87f67100000</link><description>拜登表示，他向德黑兰传达的信息是：“不要” ■ 伊朗称其扣押了“与以色列有关”的船只 ■ 以色列国防军发现失踪 14 岁以色列人尸体后，定居者在巴勒斯坦村庄发动暴行 ■ 《纽约时报》编辑委员会呼吁美国对以色列提供军事援助的条件 ■ 这是战争 190 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 17:09:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-190-iran-says-it-seized-ship-linked-to-israel/0000018e-d862-d01b-abdf-f87f67100000</guid></item><item><title>加沙谈判陷入僵局，数千人抗议政府，要求以色列各地达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal-across-county/0000018e-d7fb-de1f-a38f-dfff82c80000</link><description>特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法和贝尔谢巴正在举行示威活动。人质家属指责政府抛弃人质，呼吁将内塔尼亚胡驱逐并结束战争，“如果我们必须付出代价才能让我们的亲人活着回来”</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 17:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal-across-county/0000018e-d7fb-de1f-a38f-dfff82c80000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗革命卫队在阿联酋海岸扣押一艘与以色列有关的集装箱船</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/irans-revolutionary-guard-seizes-an-israel-linked-container-ship-off-coast-of-uae/0000018e-d7ad-d01b-abdf-ffffbda90000</link><description>伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队在伊朗和阿联酋之间的霍尔木兹海峡入口处扣押了一艘与以色列 Zodiac 集团有联系的集装箱船。该船被征用并改道前往伊朗水域。伊朗没有提供任何解释，只是说这艘船隶属于以色列</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 15:05:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/irans-revolutionary-guard-seizes-an-israel-linked-container-ship-off-coast-of-uae/0000018e-d7ad-d01b-abdf-ffffbda90000</guid></item><item><title>失踪的以色列青少年确认在西岸袭击中被谋杀；巴勒斯坦人在定居者的暴行中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/body-of-14-year-old-israeli-who-went-missing-found-netanyahu-we-will-find-the-murderers/0000018e-d737-df04-adae-fff7ff760000</link><description>一名 14 岁以色列定居者失踪几天后，他的尸体被发现。作为回应，定居者袭击了附近的巴勒斯坦村庄，袭击居民并放火焚烧财产。巴勒斯坦人报告至少八人受伤，其中一人伤势严重</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 11:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/body-of-14-year-old-israeli-who-went-missing-found-netanyahu-we-will-find-the-murderers/0000018e-d737-df04-adae-fff7ff760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列关闭所有学校，加紧准备应对伊朗袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-live/biden-doubles-down-on-iran-warning-dont-u-s-move-additional-assets-to-region/0000018e-d491-d161-ab8f-f4f583d30000</link><description>拜登返回白宫密切关注以色列与伊朗的升级 ■ 失踪的以色列青少年确认在约旦河西岸袭击中被谋杀；至少八名巴勒斯坦人在定居者的暴乱中受伤 ■ 以色列国防军宣布增援约旦河西岸部队 ■ 伊朗确认扣押“与以色列有关”的船只，并将其转移到伊朗领土 ■ 以色列国防军称，基布兹安全小组成员因黎巴嫩无人机爆炸而严重受伤 ■ 以色列国防军发言人称伊朗将为任何升级承担后果</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 02:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-live/biden-doubles-down-on-iran-warning-dont-u-s-move-additional-assets-to-region/0000018e-d491-d161-ab8f-f4f583d30000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列监狱服刑近 40 年后，瓦利德·达卡 (Walid Daqqa) 的死亡并未让他重获自由</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-almost-40-years-in-israeli-prison-death-didnt-set-walid-daqqa-free/0000018e-cda3-dc93-adce-eff3d84e0000</link><description>身患重病时，没有人告诉亲人他快要死了。自战争爆发以来，他的家人一直不被允许探望他，目前尚未收到他的遗体</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 01:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/after-almost-40-years-in-israeli-prison-death-didnt-set-walid-daqqa-free/0000018e-cda3-dc93-adce-eff3d84e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部城镇两起枪击事件致三人死亡，警方怀疑与犯罪有关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/three-killed-in-two-incidents-in-northern-israeli-towns-police-suspect-crime-related/0000018e-d4db-df04-adae-fddb866f0000</link><description>在 Kafr Yasif 的一次枪击事件中，一名男子被杀，四人受伤，其中包括他的婴儿和一名清真寺的伊玛目。随后，两名男子在伊斯菲亚村被杀，警方怀疑这是对先前事件的报复</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article/.premium/three-killed-in-two-incidents-in-northern-israeli-towns-police-suspect-crime-related/0000018e-d4db-df04-adae-fddb866f0000</guid></item><item><title>所有以色列人都必须问自己：杀害 10 万加沙人是否合法？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/all-israelis-must-ask-themselves-is-it-legitimate-to-kill-100-000-gazans/0000018e-d4d2-df04-adae-fdd27f510000</link><description>为了不辜负我们 10 月 7 日所期待的同情和团结，我们必须尽一切努力制止加沙地带的恐怖</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/all-israelis-must-ask-themselves-is-it-legitimate-to-kill-100-000-gazans/0000018e-d4d2-df04-adae-fdd27f510000</guid></item><item><title>舞者逃离哈马斯诺瓦大屠杀现场的假枪声？以色列独立日音乐录影带拍摄现场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/dancers-fleeing-fake-guns-at-hamas-massacre-site-what-israel-planned-for-independence-day/0000018e-d496-df04-adae-fdd6e11b0000</link><description>为什么一段由国家赞助的怪诞视频要在 10 月 7 日 364 名以色列人被谋杀的地方拍摄，其中包括一名流行歌手、一个舞蹈团和惊恐的失去亲人的家庭？</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:18:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/dancers-fleeing-fake-guns-at-hamas-massacre-site-what-israel-planned-for-independence-day/0000018e-d496-df04-adae-fdd6e11b0000</guid></item><item><title>“我问辛瓦尔，让一万名无辜的加沙人死去值得吗？他说，十万也值了。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-asked-sinwar-is-it-worth-10-000-gazans-dying-he-said-even-100-000-is-worth-it/0000018e-d40a-d5ed-adcf-f79af56c0000</link><description>作为以色列监狱管理局情报部门的负责人，尤瓦尔·比顿（Yuval Bitton）近距离认识哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔（Yahya Sinwar）——该组织于 10 月 7 日谋杀了比顿的侄子。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:13:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-asked-sinwar-is-it-worth-10-000-gazans-dying-he-said-even-100-000-is-worth-it/0000018e-d40a-d5ed-adcf-f79af56c0000</guid></item><item><title>下班的以色列警察因道路纠纷杀死了 50 岁男子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/off-duty-israeli-officer-kills-50-year-old-man-following-dispute-on-the-road/0000018e-d379-d45f-abcf-f37d08fc0000</link><description>以色列警方称，周五，美国大使馆一名文职雇员在一场道路争吵中，据称拿出一把刀刺伤了一名休班官员的手。这名军官随后开枪打死了这名平民</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 18:38:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/off-duty-israeli-officer-kills-50-year-old-man-following-dispute-on-the-road/0000018e-d379-d45f-abcf-f37d08fc0000</guid></item><item><title>搜寻失踪 14 岁以色列人期间发生冲突，巴勒斯坦人死亡，三名以色列士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-3-israeli-soldiers-wounded-in-clashes-during-search-for-missing-boy/0000018e-d32e-d5ed-adcf-f3be28b00000</link><description>安全部队与巴勒斯坦人在 Al-Mughayyir 镇搜寻 14 岁的 Binyhamin Ahimeir 时爆发冲突，Binyhamin Ahimeir 在离开前哨站放牧牲畜后失踪</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-3-israeli-soldiers-wounded-in-clashes-during-search-for-missing-boy/0000018e-d32e-d5ed-adcf-f3be28b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 189 天：哈马斯哈尼亚称儿子被杀不会影响停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-189-hamas-haniyeh-says-sons-killing-wont-affect-truce-talks/0000018e-d316-d5ed-adcf-f396502c0000</link><description>法国、英国、加拿大、印度、波兰和澳大利亚向以色列、约旦河西岸、伊朗和黎巴嫩发出旅行警告 ■ 国防部长加兰特会见美国中央司令部负责人 ■ 欧盟对哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织的军事部门实施制裁 ■ 哈马斯政治领导人哈尼亚表示儿子被杀不会影响停战谈判 ■ 寻找失踪的 14 岁以色列人，约旦河西岸爆发冲突 ■ 战争结束 189 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-189-hamas-haniyeh-says-sons-killing-wont-affect-truce-talks/0000018e-d316-d5ed-adcf-f396502c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的鲁莽已成为内塔尼亚胡的政策选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-recklessness-has-become-netanyahus-policy-of-choice/0000018e-d243-df04-adae-ffd335120000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡多年来未能起草伊朗政策，现在他拒绝概述加沙战后战略。完全是为了迎合内部政治目标，才导致战争中的轻率轰炸</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:17:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-recklessness-has-become-netanyahus-policy-of-choice/0000018e-d243-df04-adae-ffd335120000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判中证人的苦难表明总理对以色列的腐败有多深</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/witness-ordeal-in-netanyahu-trial-shows-how-deeply-the-pm-has-corrupted-israel/0000018e-d149-df04-adae-fddb13780000</link><description>警察准将。敢于挑战内塔尼亚胡的科雷什·巴努尔将军为自己的职业生涯付出了代价——本周在法庭上，他遭到了法官的严厉质问和冷遇。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/witness-ordeal-in-netanyahu-trial-shows-how-deeply-the-pm-has-corrupted-israel/0000018e-d149-df04-adae-fddb13780000</guid></item><item><title>支持内塔尼亚胡的抗议者因“比比是杀人犯”的标语而殴打耶路撒冷居民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/pro-netanyahu-protesters-punch-jerusalem-resident-over-bibi-is-a-murderer-sign/0000018e-d17f-df04-adae-fdfff90a0000</link><description>在该男子阻止他们攻击他挂起标语的妻子后，示威者高喊种族主义口号。警方将双方分开并没有逮捕任何人</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:15:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/pro-netanyahu-protesters-punch-jerusalem-resident-over-bibi-is-a-murderer-sign/0000018e-d17f-df04-adae-fdfff90a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在约旦河西岸冲突中打死两名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-two-palestinians-in-west-bank-clashes/0000018e-d197-d01b-abdf-f9ff445f0000</link><description>以色列国防军证实已击毙穆罕默德·奥马尔·达拉格梅，据他们称，他指挥了恐怖活动。他的父亲是哈马斯成员，10 月 7 日后被捕，两周后在以色列拘留期间死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:47:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-two-palestinians-in-west-bank-clashes/0000018e-d197-d01b-abdf-f9ff445f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>